title: Chelsea Peretti And Jordan Peele Are Expecting A Child — And Their 'Announcement' Is SO Funny!
text:
2/05/2017 4:59   TV News • Baby Blabber • Beyonce • Cute! • Family • Pregnant • Cuteness! • A • Baby Bump Watch • Pregnancy Talk • Cute Kidz • Cute and Contemporary Families • Instagram • Heartwarming • Pregnancy Style 
This is wonderful — so happy for these two!!! 
Chelsea Peretti and Jordan Peele are expecting their first child together, according to an announcement they made on Instagram yesterday, and knowing how funny both of 'em are, well, you could just expect their big reveal to be witty! 
And it was! The TV and comedy stars decided to make a little light of the much-covered Beyoncé pregnancy announcement with a not-so-big reveal of their own, on Peretti's IG account! 
Ch-ch-check it out (below)!!! 
beyonce schmonce A photo posted by Chelsea Peretti (@chelsanity) on Feb 4, 2017 at 3:12pm PST 
Too funny! That caption is PERFECT!! 
And too cute! 
We are so happy for these two, even if their baby bump announcement wasn't quite as… glamorous… as Queen Bey! Ha!!
